      <article data-history-node-id="37235" about="/the-interpreter/us-india-relations-are-shaken-not-shattered" class="node-type-interpreter-debate">

  
    

  <div class="interpreter-article-detail archive-detail-page node-type-interpreter-debate">
	<div class="container pv-lg">
		<div class="article-masthead row txt-center">
			<div class="article-title col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-8 pv-sm">
				<h1 class="txt-f4 txt-s7 balance-text">US-India relations are shaken but not shattered</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="article-author pv-md col-sm-offset-3 col-sm-6">
															<a class="txt-dn txt-f1 txt-s3 txt-tu" href="/the-interpreter/contributors/articles/michael-kugelman">
							Michael Kugelman
						</a>
												</div>
							<div class="article-summary col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-10">
					<p class="txt-s5 txt-f1 balance-text txt-lmd">
						An alleged plot by an Indian official to assassinate an American is a gut punch – but strategic choices will prevail.
					</p>
				</div>
					</div>

		<div class="article-main-image">
			<img class="article-main-image-img" src="https://www.lowyinstitute.org/sites/default/files/styles/interpreter_article_image/public/2023-12/GettyImages-1258976347.jpg?itok=9gJTdkBP" alt="Despite having known of the alleged plot, the White House didn’t cancel upcoming high-level engagements with New Delhi (Brendan Smialowski/AFP via Getty Images)">
              <div class="article-save-btn">
          
        </div>
      							<div class="article-main-image-caption">
					Despite having known of the alleged plot, the White House didn’t cancel upcoming high-level engagements with New Delhi (Brendan Smialowski/AFP via Getty Images)
				</div>
					</div>

		<div class="clearfix">
			<div class="txt-center pv-md">
				<span class="txt-muted">
					Published 20 Dec 2023&nbsp;
				</span>

									<ul class="article-tags d-ib list-unstyled">
													<li class="article-tag d-ib">
								<a href="/the-interpreter/archive?issue=321" class="txt-muted txt-dn">
									India
								</a>
							</li>
													<li class="article-tag d-ib">
								<a href="/the-interpreter/archive?issue=217" class="txt-muted txt-dn">
									United States
								</a>
							</li>
											</ul>
				
								
									&emsp;
					<span class="rm-twiter-acc https://twitter.com/@michaelkugelman ">
